-- Eric Bensoussan Joins Nomura as European Equity Structuring Head
-- B y   A l a s t a i r   M a r s h
-- 2013-08-06T15:59:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-06/eric-bensoussan-joins-nomura-as-european-equity-structuring-head.html
Nomura Holdings Inc. (8604)  has hired Eric Bensoussan as head of equity structuring for Europe, the Middle
East and Africa, according to Angharad White, a London-based
spokeswoman for the bank.  Bensoussan previously worked at  UBS AG (UBSN)  where he was the
European head of equity structuring in  London . He has also led
similar teams at Deutsche Bank AG and Credit Lyonnais SA, which
merged with  Credit Agricole SA (ACA)  in 2003.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alastair Marsh in London at 
